<div id="home"
     data-top="background-position: 50% 50%;"
     data-top-center="background-position: 50% 30%;"
     >
  <div class="overlay">
    <div style="display: table-cell;
    vertical-align: middle;">
      <div class="spacing visible-xs-block"></div>
      <h1
          data--200-bottom-top="color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0);"
          data--100-bottom-top="color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 1.0);"
          data-anchor-target="#new-world > div">
      <span class="bold">Imagine a world in which all human beings flourish.</span><br/><br/>


      A world with <span class="bold">equal opportunity.</span> And <span class="bold">education, universal health care, world peace, thriving community, environmental responsibility, and collective decision-making.</span><br/><br/>

      <span class="bold">Let's make it happen.</span>
      </h1>
      <div class="spacing visible-xs-block"></div>
    </div>

  </div>
</div>


<div id="spacing"></div>
<div id="new-world" name="#new-world" data-menu-offset="-9">
  <div>
    <hr
      data-50-top="border-color: rgb(217, 83, 79);"
      data-100-top="border-color: rgb(51, 51, 51);"
      data-anchor-target="#new-world > div"     
        />
    <h1 class="bold fancy"
        data-50-top="color: rgb(217, 83, 79);"
        data-100-top="color: rgb(51, 51, 51);"
        data-anchor-target="#new-world > div"><span>New World</span></h1>
    <p>Ever since the beginning of our time, poverty, malnutrition, and environmental exploitation have been part of the human story. They have been around for so long that many have stopped questioning their presence, even though there is nothing natural about them. In fact, there is overwhelming scientific evidence that our planet provides sufficient resources for all of us.<br/><br/>

  Currently, over three billion people live on less than $2.50 a day, the world's richest 80 people own as much wealth as the bottom 50% of humanity, and by 2030 we will have irreversibly damaged the environment our life so essentially depends upon.<br/><br/>
      
      Now imagine what our world could be. If every human being got to unfold their talent and achieve greatness. If ... If ... This world would be one massively thriving, abundant, and beautiful celebration of life.<br/><br/>
      
  We know that creating this world is possible, so let's make it happen.</p>

    <div role="tabpanel">
      <div class="row">

        <% hover_icons = ["icon-users", "icon-coin-dollar", "icon-library", "icon-peace", "icon-leaf", "icon-heart"] %>
        <% hover_icons.each_with_index do |icon, i| %>
          <div class="col-xs-4 col-sm-4 col-md-2 col-lg-2">
            <div id="new-world_icon_<%= i %>" class="hover-icon<%= i == 0 ? ' active' : '' %>">
              <i class="round-icon">
                <span class="<%= icon %>" aria-hidden="true"></span>
              </i>
            </div>
          </div>
        <% end %>

      </div>
      <div class="tab-content">
        <div class="tab-pane well activated in">
            <span class="heading bold  emphasis">Society</span>
            We are establishing a society in which <span class="bold emphasis">everyone can thrive</span>. People have <span class="bold emphasis">absolute freedom</span> over how they spend their life. The <span class="bold emphasis">provision of basic needs</span> - food, water, shelter, health care, education - is always guaranteed. 
        </div>
        <div class="tab-pane well">
          <span class="heading bold emphasis">Economy</span>
          We are creating an economy that <span class="bold emphasis">maximizes social and environmental profits</span>. Financial profits are <span class="bold emphasis">shared among all of us</span>. Every company upholds standards of <span class="bold emphasis">sustainability, transparency, and ethicality</span>.
        </div>
        <div class="tab-pane well">
          <span class="heading bold emphasis">Politics</span>
          We are committed to an <span class="bold emphasis">equal power structure</span>: a system in which every individual has the same amount of political decision-making power. <span class="bold emphasis">Decisions are made collectively and directly</span> by the individuals who will be affected by them.
        </div>
        <div class="tab-pane well">
          <span class="heading bold emphasis">Peace</span>
          We are dedicated to creating a <span class="bold emphasis">peaceful planet Earth</span>, on which people of different value systems live together in harmony and collaboration. <span class="bold emphasis">Safety of mental and physical health</span> is guaranteed. We resolve conflict through <span class="bold emphasis">collectively developing solutions</span> with all involved parties.
        </div>
        <div class="tab-pane well">
          <span class="heading bold emphasis">Sustainability</span>
          We are devoted to cultivating <span class="bold emphasis">healthy and flourishing ecosystems</span>. The <span class="bold emphasis">well-being of nature</span> is essential for our lives and the lives of future generations. We recognize dependence on the environment as a <span class="bold emphasis">great privilege as well as a great responsibility</span>.
        </div>
        <div class="tab-pane well">
          <span class="heading bold emphasis">Culture</span>
          We are fostering a culture based on <span class="bold emphasis">community and collaboration</span>. All human beings are enabled, encouraged, and empowered to <span class="bold emphasis">follow their hearts and realize their dreams</span>.
        </div>        
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<div id="action-plan" data-menu-offset="-9">
  <div>
    <hr
      data-50-top="border-color: rgb(217, 83, 79);"
      data-100-top="border-color: rgb(51, 51, 51);"
      data-anchor-target="#action-plan > div"     
        />
    <h1 class="bold fancy"
      data-50-top="color: rgb(217, 83, 79);"
      data-100-top="color: rgb(51, 51, 51);"
      data-anchor-target="#action-plan > div"><span>Action Plan</span></h1>

    
    <p>For most of our history, we have put the fate of the world into the hands of a few individuals - kings, dictators, presidents. Some of them have led with great heart and courage, but the conclusion is unambiguous: Our world today is far from its full potential.<br/><br/>
      
      Never before in history have ordinary people - like you and I - had . <br/><br/>
      
      The time has come to put the fate of the world back into our hands. This planet belongs to all of us and so all of us together will decide what we want our world to look like.</p><br/>

    <div class="panel panel-default">
      <div class="icon">
        <span class="icon-personal"></span>
      </div>
      <div class="panel-heading">
        <h3 class="panel-title bold">Personal Change <span class="label label-danger">Step 1</span></h3>
      </div>
      <div class="panel-quote">
        <quote>"Be the change you want to see in the world." &mdash; Gandhi</quote>
      </div>
      <div class="panel-body">
        <p>All change starts with the individual. And there is a lot that each of us can do.<br/><br/>
        
          In the first stage, Neonia will become a resource hub for changing our personal lives. We will offer alternatives to traditional banks, listings of ethical businesses, .... Toolkits to transform yourself and your community.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    
    <div class="arrow">
      <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-chevron-down"></span>
    </div>
    
    <div class="panel panel-default">
      <div class="icon">
        <span class="icon-systemic"></span>
      </div>
      <div class="panel-heading">
        <h3 class="panel-title bold">Systemic Change <span class="label label-danger">Step 2</span></h3>
      </div>
      <div class="panel-quote">
        <quote>"The secret of change is to focus all of your energy, not on fighting the old, but on building the new." &mdash; Aristotle</quote>
      </div>
      <div class="panel-body">
        <p>The problems that we see on our planet - poverty, malnutrition, environmental exploitation - are systemic. They are the direct consequences of the societal, economic, and political systems that we operate the world on. Systems putting financial profits above anything, creating hierachies of political power, and fostering cultures of individualism and competition.<br/><br/>
        
        It is time to invent a new generation of societal, economic, and political systems. Systems that ...<br/><br/>
        
        To do so, we will build Neonia - a global, borderless, online country dedicated to empowering every human being to flourish. We will implement our own decision-making processes, our own rules for a new economic system, and we will foster a culture based on community and collaboration.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    
    <div class="arrow">
      <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-chevron-down"></span>
    </div>
    
    <div class="panel panel-default">
      <div class="icon">
        <span class="icon-global"></span>
      </div>
      <div class="panel-heading">
        <h3 class="panel-title bold">Global Change <span class="label label-danger">Step 3</span></h3>
      </div>
      <div class="panel-quote">
        <quote>"When injustice becomes law, resistance becomes duty." &mdash; Thomas Jefferson</quote>
      </div>
      <div class="panel-body">
        <p>We refuse to accept the systemic oppression that is so evident in poverty, war, and environmental exploitation around the globe. We are committed to ending this oppression through collaboration and peaceful conflict resolution.<br/><br/>
          
          Neonia will be open to all human beings. Yet, we recognize that there are many different ways of living life and every human being must have the right to individually decide what type of government they want to live in.<br/><br/>
          
          Neonia is an easily reproducable model to create many diverse nations with diverse types of government. As long as their objective is to empower humanity to flourish, we will work closely together with all of them. Furthermore, every human being must, at any time, have the freedom to leave one nation and join any other.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<div id="join-us" data-menu-offset="-9">
  <div>
    <hr
      data-50-top="border-color: rgb(217, 83, 79);"
      data-100-top="border-color: rgb(51, 51, 51);"
      data-anchor-target="#join-us > div"     
        />
    <h1 class="bold fancy"
        data-50-top="color: rgb(217, 83, 79);"
        data-100-top="color: rgb(51, 51, 51);"
        data-anchor-target="#join-us > div"><span>Join us</span></h1>
    
    
    <%= form_for @user, url: {action: "signup"} do |f| %>
      <%= f.text_field :name %>
      <%= f.text_field :email %>
      <%= f.submit "Create" %>
